And I spent more time with her off the set at her home than at the studio, he said. I signed a seven-year contract with the studio in 1956 and the first episode I was in was aired that December with Bob Hope _ I just turned 6. I think the thing I remember most about Lucy was that she was very much in control of everything, said Thibodeaux, who began playing the drums at age 2, was a professional drummer at age 4 and is now drummer with David and the Giants, a Christian rock group. 